Usage: setWhatIfPortPriority [-help] [-driveCell  | -portParam ]

-help          # Prints out the command usage
-driveCell     # Specifies that the values set through the setWhatIfDriveType
               # command will take precedence (bool, optional)
-portParam     # Specifies that the values set through the
               # setWhatIfPortParameters command will take precedence
               # (bool, optional)